.mcp-deep-dive.py-5
  .container
    %h2.text-center.mb-5 How Fast-MCP Gem Powers Our Intelligence
    
    .row.mb-4.align-items-center
      .col-md-6.mb-4
        %h3.h4 
          %i.fas.fa-cogs.text-primary.me-2
          High-Performance Architecture
        %p.lead
          The fast-mcp gem provides optimized Ruby bindings for Model Context Protocol:
        .code-example.bg-dark.text-light.p-3.rounded
          %pre.mb-0
            %code.text-success
              = "# Natural language to business intelligence"
              %br
              = 'query = "Show revenue trends for Q3 electronics"'
              %br
              %span.text-info
                = "# Fast-MCP processes context and relationships"
              %br
              = "result = MCPProcessor.analyze(query, context: :sales)"
              %br
              %span.text-warning
                = "# Returns structured insights with correlations"
      
      .col-md-6.mb-4
        %img.img-fluid.rounded.shadow{src: "/images/mcp-processing-flow.svg", alt: "MCP Processing Flow"}

    .row.mb-4.align-items-center
      .col-md-6.mb-4.order-md-2
        %h3.h4 
          %i.fas.fa-network-wired.text-primary.me-2
          Context-Aware Data Processing
        %p.lead
          Advanced relationship mapping and pattern recognition:
        %ul.list-unstyled
          %li.mb-2 
            %i.fas.fa-check-circle.text-success.me-2
            %strong Cross-referential analysis:
            Links orders, products, and customer behavior automatically
          %li.mb-2 
            %i.fas.fa-check-circle.text-success.me-2
            %strong Intelligent correlation discovery:
            Finds hidden patterns in business data
          %li.mb-2 
            %i.fas.fa-check-circle.text-success.me-2
            %strong Self-improving algorithms:
            Learns from query patterns to enhance accuracy
          %li.mb-0 
            %i.fas.fa-check-circle.text-success.me-2
            %strong Real-time processing:
            Delivers insights in milliseconds, not minutes
      
      .col-md-6.mb-4.order-md-1
        %img.img-fluid.rounded.shadow{src: "/images/context-mapping.svg", alt: "Context Mapping"}

.serpapi-deep-dive.bg-light.py-5
  .container
    %h2.text-center.mb-5 How SerpAPI Powers Real-Time Travel Search
    
    .row.mb-4.align-items-center
      .col-md-6.mb-4
        %h3.h4 
          %i.fas.fa-hotel.text-primary.me-2
          Hotels & Restaurants Intelligence
        %p.lead
          Advanced location-based search with comprehensive coverage:
        .bg-white.p-3.rounded.border
          %h6.text-primary.mb-2 Search Process:
          %ol.mb-3
            %li 
              %strong Location Resolution:
              GPS coordinates lookup from 300+ Indian cities
            %li 
              %strong SerpAPI Query:
              Real-time Google Maps data via optimized API calls
            %li 
              %strong Data Processing:
              Structured formatting with ratings, reviews, and pricing
            %li 
              %strong Smart Fallback:
              Demo data if API unavailable, ensuring uninterrupted service
          .small.text-muted
            %i.fas.fa-info-circle.me-1
            Covers Mumbai, Delhi, Bangalore, Chennai, Hyderabad, and 295+ more cities
      
      .col-md-6.mb-4
        %img.img-fluid.rounded.shadow{src: "/images/hotel-search-flow.svg", alt: "Hotel Search Process"}

    .row.mb-4.align-items-center
